 <span data-ttu-id="e7cfd-315">Im folgenden Beispiel werden Informationen zu einem <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>-Objekt in die [Konsole](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159613)geschrieben.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e7cfd-315">The following example writes information about a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object to the [console](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159613).</span></span>  
  
